Arvin Industries Inc raise 150 mln dlrs offering 8-3/8 pct 10-year note 9-1/8 pct 30-year sinking fund debentures. Lead underwriter offering 75 mln dlrs Merrill Lynch Capital Markets. The note price 99.63 pct yield 8.43 pct debenture price 99.54 pct yield 9.17 pct. The note redeemable par Arvin's option March 1 1994. The debenture redeemable non-refundable March 1 1997. Both rat BAA-2 Moody's Investors Service BBB Standard Poor's. Reuter 